*****************
 1. INSTALLATION
*****************

Just put all files in a directory that is on PATH.
vs2make2 requires Perl version 5.6 or later.

*****************
 2. HOW TO USE
*****************

Copy your Visual Studio projects to a Linux environment.
Run vs2make2 at the project root. Do the command line below to
see the document.

$ perldoc vs2make2

